# Website (generated at build time by `tsx scripts/build-catalog.ts` and
# `vite build`, both run by .github/workflows/deploy-website.yml before
# the Pages upload). Kept out of git to avoid noisy diffs and keep
# data/skill-index/*.json (catalog) + website-src/ (React app) as the
# single sources of truth.
